sentences: Her debut album She's Not From Around Here, produced by Grammy winner Dan Schlissel, was released June 26, 2020 on Stand Up!
After living in New York City and Los Angeles as a photographer, Maybury moved to Minneapolis, where she began performing stand-up in 2013.
Since 2017, she has co-hosted Day Drinking with Mom, a standup showcase focusing on parenting.
